data.text:
My new games:

European Cup of champions 1963/1964:

eighth final/ 2nd leg:

Borussia Dortmund - Benfica Lissabon/ Lisboa 5:0 German/ black-white

German football-championship 1963:

last final before foundation of German league Bundesliga 1964:

Borussia Dortmund - 1.FC Köln 3:1 German/ black-white

Champions League 2010/2011:

2nd qualification round/ 1st leg

Red Bull Salzburg - HB Torshavn (Faroer Islands) 5:0 German

Europa League 2010/2011:

2nd qualification round/ 1st leg

Austria Wien/ Vienna - NK Siroki Brijeg (Bosnia-Herzegovina) 2:2 German

World Cup 1962 in Chile:

Brazil - Czechoslovaquia 3:1 BBC-Version/ black-white

World Cup 1990 in Italy:

qualification:

Austria - Iceland 2:1 German

Austria - USSR 0:0 German

Austria - GDR 3:0 German

World Cup 2010 in South Africa

All games from Austrian TV-channel ORF with live commentary.

I am looking for games with German commentary I don't have.

Specially I am looking for game of Preliminaries in WC 1990:

Uruguay - South Korea 1:0

In German from ARD/ ZDF/ ORF or Eurosport.

World Cup 1974:

Sweden - Uruguay 3:0 ARD/ ZDF/ ORF or only stadium sound.

I have a bad version and look for a better one.

My complete collection on http://footballdreams.dreipage2.de .

Hey guys....Just back from vacation. I'm looking for 1990, 1994 and 1998 World Cup matches from UNIVISION, with Andres Cantor and Norberto Longo in the booth. I'm especially looking for:

1990 World Cup - Romania vs USSR, Spanish, UNIVISION

1990 World Cup - Argentina vs USSR, Spanish, UNIVISION

1990 World Cup - England vs Ireland, Spanish, UNIVISION

1990 World Cup - Spain vs Uruguay, Spanish, UNIVISION

1990 World Cup - Italy vs USA, Spanish, UNIVISION

1990 World Cup - Holland vs England, Spanish, UNIVISION

1990 World Cup - Brasil vs Costa Rica, Spanish, UNIVISION

1994 World Cup - Germany vs Bolivia, Spanish, UNIVISION

1998 World Cup - Holland vs Belgium, Spanish, UNIVISION

If you have even just one of these, or any others 1990, 1994, 1998 World Cup from UNIVISION, please let me know.

I am also looking for 1990 - 1999 Champions League matches

in ENGLSH. Especially early rounds.

Send me your list and I'll send you mine if you're interested in a trade.

I'm always looking for new trading contacts and partners.

Thanks!

Joe

JOEYMZLL@AOL.com
